00:54.120 --> 00:57.320
 Dr. Deisseroth's laboratory has pioneered the development

00:57.320 --> 00:59.440
 and use of what are called channelopsins,

00:59.440 --> 01:01.620
 proteins that come from algae,

01:01.620 --> 01:04.300
 which can now be introduced to the nervous systems

01:04.300 --> 01:07.480
