47:17.180 --> 47:19.900
 and the current state of your work

47:19.900 --> 47:21.900
 in the laboratory in the clinic,

47:21.900 --> 47:24.420
 and an interaction with a patient.

47:24.420 --> 47:28.300
 So this is, as I recall, a woman who was severely depressed.

