48:00.700 --> 48:02.240
 Or to manipulate, for instance,

48:02.240 --> 48:04.820
 a very small localized region of the brain.

48:04.820 --> 48:07.380
 Let me frame it a little bit differently

48:07.380 --> 48:08.380
 in light of what we were talking about

48:08.380 --> 48:09.580
 a couple of minutes ago.

